    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... that's a really dark way to put it. But honestly, it's exactly how it feels. Like I'm just existing for no reason. It's like the person I was died with him, and this version of me is just... stuck. Do you really think it's just a pointless ritual?",
